# Project Context Rules

At the start of every new conversation:
1. Read docs/CURRENT_STAGE.md and docs/structure.md before doing anything
2. Confirm context is loaded
3. Do not hallucinate about project structure or code

After every change:
1. Update docs/CURRENT_STAGE.md per the context-keeper skill
2. Update docs/CHANGELOG_AI.md with details
3. Update docs/structure.md if files were created/deleted

После любых правок docs/SisPrompt.md, docs/CURRENT_STAGE.md, docs/CHANGELOG_AI.md, docs/structure.md — из корня проекта выполнить: php scripts/sync-docs-to-txt.php
